{"tid":651124,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【紅隧廣告玩不文】《死侍2》繼續三級 「更粗 更長 更大 更硬」","createTime":"2018-05-03T00:48:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T14:08:06.000Z","uid":41343,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8606bbd53cc7bff0368046b9531357f4f4a07dea","tid":651124,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T00:48:46.000Z","msg":"由賴恩雷諾士（Ryan Reynolds）主演嘅《死侍2》（Deadpool 2）本月上映，今次加入更多新角色，又係有別一貫超級英雄以抵死情節吸引觀眾，香港方面已定為三級片上映。<br />\n<br />\n《復仇者聯盟3: 無限之戰》(Avengers: Infinity War)熱潮停不了，嚟緊相信都會繼續係英雄片世界，緊接上映嘅《死侍2》，呢幾日喺紅隧九龍入口，已經見到好大幅宣傳海報。同上集一樣被電檢評定為三級，未夠18歲唔可以睇住，而佢幅海報亦都配合三級主題，宣傳句語係「更粗 更長 更大 更硬」，簡直令人想入非非。不過睇真啲原來後而仲有粒細字跟尾，變成「更粗鄙 更長氣 更大牌 更硬淨」。電影公司方面透露，原本嘅構想係「今舖更大支嘢，玩到你闊過紅隧」，配合放喺紅隧口嘅氣勢，不過牽涉到其他公司，所以最後放棄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180502/large/1525250005_1115.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180502%2Flarge%2F1525250005_1115.jpg&h=f5657dc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180502/large/1525250046_7e60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180502%2Flarge%2F1525250046_7e60.jpg&h=25c811cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c068116061d56accbc2b603d05bf45f825fbfdc8","tid":651124,"uid":14333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T00:51:29.000Z","msg":"屌你又想點呀 又想話思想不良呀？"},{"pid":"642d8bb7bc5ec15fa87cb8de67a0fb41d4ac97f3","tid":651124,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c068116061d56accbc2b603d05bf45f825fbfdc8","tid":651124,"uid":14333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T00:51:29.000Z","msg":"屌你又想點呀 又想話思想不良呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T01:21:14.000Z","msg":"有啲咁嘅事？"},{"pid":"0a1aa07c4b908319140e67b66f2e1bb5f1361baa","tid":651124,"uid":71770,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201